name: The Mountains Call x Stoic The Photographer

metadata.name: Head West
metadata.description:
The Rocky Mountains of Canada, a sight to behold. From my hometown the mountains are in my backyard, always there. To me this image captures a feeling of wanting to break out of my town and head west to the Rockies. 

I never appreciated them growing up, but now I see just how amazing and lucky I am to be near them. If you collect this I hope you find the same desire to see them like I do.

Just head west.
